{"article_id":"y3qJWk0dbsXAkgT8","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"As coronavirus infections continue to rise in a number of states across the country","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"some health experts are warning","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"that the second wave of COVID-19 in the U.S. is already taking place .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"\" I think","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"the second wave has begun , \"","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"William Schaffner , an infectious diseases expert and professor at Vanderbilt University Medical Center , told CNBC Monday .","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"\" We are opening up across the country ,","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"but many , many people are not social distancing ,","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"many are not wearing their masks","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"and those are the things","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"that will contribute to coronavirus spreading , \"","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"Schaffner said .","depth":3},{"id":12,"text":"America is changing FASTER THAN EVER .","depth":4},{"id":13,"text":"Add Changing America to your Facebook and Twitter feeds","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"to stay engaged on the latest news and smartest insights .","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"Weeks after lifting stay-at-home orders ,","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"some states are experiencing record numbers of cases and hospitalizations .","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"South Carolina and Alabama both hit single-day records of new confirmed cases Sunday ,","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"while Texas is seeing record numbers of hospitalizations .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"Meanwhile , Oregon last week put a temporary pause on all further reopening efforts after a spike in single-day cases .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"New York Gov . Andrew Cuomo","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"( D )","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"on Sunday threatened to halt the reopening of Manhattan and the Hamptons over complaints","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"people are flouting social distancing guidance .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"New York so far is not among the states","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"currently seeing an increase in cases and hospitalizations .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"HERE ARE THE 6 WAYS","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"THE CORONAVIRUS PANDEMIC COULD END COUNTRIES","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"LED BY WOMEN","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"HAVE FARED BETTER AGAINST CORONAVIRUS .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"WHY ?","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"6 FEET OF DISTANCE MAY NOT BE ENOUGH","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"TO STOP SPREAD OF CORONAVIRUS","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"Schaffner also warned","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"that many people are continuing to gather in large groups","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"and are not being cautious .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"\" People are going to religious services on the weekends ,","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"and many people are simply not being careful ,","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"they ' re being carefree ,","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"and that of course will lead to more spread of the COVID virus , \"","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Schaffner said .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"The health expert went on to say","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"the chance of another lockdown is \" off the table , \" due to the economic and social effects","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"prompted by the first lockdown .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"instead , government , business and religious leaders should work together","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"to promote the wearing of masks and social distancing .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"\" If we all do that in respect of each other ,","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"then I think","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"we can make some progress , \"","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"Schaffner told CNBC .","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"\" If we do all the opposite","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"- if we open up ,","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"do not have social distancing ,","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"don ' t wear masks","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"and congregate in large numbers again ,","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"we are going to be very stressed in the medical care system . \"","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"Schaffner ' s claim about a second wave has been disputed by other health experts","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"who say","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"the U.S. has yet to close the book on the first wave .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"America is in a historic fight .","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"Add Changing America to your Facebook and Twitter feeds","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"to stay engaged on the latest news and smartest insights .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"Ian Lipkin , a professor of epidemiology and director of the Center for Infection and Immunity at Columbia University , told CNBC","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"for there to be a second wave","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"the virus would need to retreat","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"and reappear ,","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"or a new variant would have to emerge .","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"\" The recent increase in cases does not reflect either , \"","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"Lipkin told the outlet .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"Other health professionals say","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"the first wave is likely to continue to drag on for some time .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"\" We really never quite finished the first wave , \"","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"Ashish Jah , a professor of global health at Harvard University , told NPR last week .","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"\" And it doesn ' t look like we are going to anytime soon . \"","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"The U.S. leads the rest of the world in the number of coronavirus cases .","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"More than 2 million cases have been recorded with more than 115,000 deaths ,","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"according to Johns Hopkins University data .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"CORONAVIRUS IS 'SPREADING LIKE WILDFIRE ' IN ARIZONA ,","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"SAYS STATE REPRESENTATIVE","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"WHO :","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"THERE 'S NO EVIDENCE","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"WEARING A MASK WILL PROTECT YOU FROM CORONAVIRUS","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"FAUCI PREDICTS ANOTHER CORONAVIRUS OUTBREAK IN THE FALL WITH A 'VERY DIFFERENT ' OUTCOME","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"MICHIGAN BARBER","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"WHO DISOBEYED STAY-AT-HOME RESTRICTIONS","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"ORDERED TO CLOSE SHOP","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"TEXAS REPORTS SINGLE-DAY HIGH IN CORONAVIRUS DEATHS","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"TWO WEEKS AFTER REOPENING","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":177,"left":100,"right":176,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":94,"right":99,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":91,"right":93,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":0,"right":90,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":90,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":93,"left":92,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":99,"left":98,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":6,"right":97,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":97,"left":95,"right":96,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":96,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":176,"left":113,"right":175,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":113,"left":102,"right":112,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":102,"left":12,"right":101,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":101,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":103,"right":111,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"N